<body>
    <div class="m-8 bg-grey-50 ">
        <div class="relative w-full max-w-lg">
            <header>
                <div class="snowflakes" aria-hidden="true">
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❅
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❆
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❅
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❆
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❅
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❆
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❅
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❆
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❅
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❆
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❅
                    </div>
                    <div class="snowflake">
                        ❆
                    </div>
                </div>
            </header>

            <div id="circle1"
                class="absolute top-0 -left-4 w-72 h-72 bg-baby-blue-lighter rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-30 animate-blob">
            </div>
            <div id="circle2"
                class="absolute top-0 -right-4 w-72 h-72 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-30 animate-blob animation-delay-2000">
            </div>
            <div id="circle3"
                class="absolute -bottom-2 w-72 h-72 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-30 animate-blob animation-delay-4000">
            </div>
            <div id="text">
                <div id="flex container" class="flex justify-center">
                    <h1 style='margin:0in;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;' class="text-5xl font-semibold">What is a
                        Secret
                        Santa?</h1>
                </div>
                <br>
                <p style='margin:0in;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;' class="text-2xl">
                    For those not familiar with
                    Secret Santa.
                    it&rsquo;s a way of spicing up the routine of gift-giving by randomizing the recipients and
                    keeping
                    all that
                    information anonymous between one another.
                </p>
                <br>
                <p style='margin:0in;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;' class="text-2xl">
                    It&apos;s commonly used during Christmas time by co-workers in an office, school classrooms, and
                    about any one with a group of three plus. Hence the term Secret Santa but it can be applied to
                    any
                    gift giving event with multiple people.
                </p>
                <p style='margin:0in;font-size:16px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</p>
                <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold" style='margin:0in;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;'>How does it
                    work?</h1>
                <br>
                <p style='margin:0in;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;' class="text-2xl">
                    We&rsquo;ve made it simple to
                    ensure that
                    you
                    can get out that list as soon as possible to ensure everyone has time to plan out their holiday
                    ideas.
                    It&rsquo;s as simple as creating a group for this holiday year. Setting up the users that you want
                    to
                    include.
                    Going to your group&apos;s page, randomizing, and clicking the button Secret Santa Me! This will
                    email
                    everyone
                    on
                    the list their recipient for this holiday!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="m-10 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold text-center ">Ready to get Started?</h1>
        <p class="m-2 font-semibold">Start setting up your participants!</p>
        <button
            class="bg-baby-blue-lighter hover:bg-baby-blue-dark font-bold py-2 px-4 border border-blue-700 rounded"><a
                asp-controller="Users" asp-action="Index">Create Participants</a></button>
    </div>
    <div class="m-8 text-left">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Already have a list of participants?</h2>
        <br>
        <button
            class="bg-baby-blue-lighter hover:bg-baby-blue-dark font-bold py-2 px-4 border border-blue-700 rounded"><a
                asp-controller="Groups" asp-action="Index">View Groups</a></button>
    </div>
    <div class="m-8">
        <hr class="">
        <footer class=" text-center font-semibold text-sm text-gold2 mt-8">
            <a class="hover:text-gold text-black" href="https://github.com/TechGlue">
                <p class="mt-1">Built by Luís :)</p>
            </a>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>